Attached you will find SHOWzOS 8.02. It should fix all known bugs.

1. Unzip
2. Binary transfer to your dino (FB80)
3. Tso receive inda
4. Run Job SHOWMACS
5. Assemble and execute SHOWzOS
6. Provide Feedback
7. tyvm

